# Common Source Amplifier

Tool: Cadence Virtuoso

## Objective
To design and simulate a common source amplifier.

## Components Used
- MOSFET
- Resistors
- Power supply

## Working Principle
The common source amplifier provides high voltage gain and inverts the input signal.

## Work Done
- Designed schematic
- Performed simulation
- Observed input and output waveforms

## Result
The amplifier successfully amplified the input signal.
